About
Our History
Docie’s Dock has been a staple in this wonderful community since 1981! We are the oldest bar in Downtown Fort Walton Beach, located in what was once Staff’s Restaurant (1913-2013). Docie’s Dock has always been a favorite among locals where they come to gather in a nice atmosphere, enjoying good times with friends while enjoying the coldest beer in town, a nice glass of wine or a savory cocktail.
Docie’s Dock features the best live music in the area, Thursday thru Saturday nights—everything from solo artists to full bands! We offer a great happy hour and daily drink specials, as well as one of the areas best Bourbon and Whiskey selections. Whether you are a local or a temporary local, we encourage you to stop in and see what we are all about.
Have Fun
Unforgettable experiences
